Serverlux is proud to announce that we are ready to launch our VPS products.
 
&lt;p&gt;We will be giving out 200 beta accounts within the next 4 Weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All VPS accounts will terminate after 1 Month, but you can renew it for a special discount price.&lt;/p&gt;
 

**The beta accounts are completely free of charge**
 
 
&lt;p&gt;All our nodes run on Raid10 and are located at the Accelerated datacenter in Frankfort on the Main.&lt;/p&gt;
 
 
&lt;p&gt;
** All beta VPS will come with:**&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4 Cores&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2048 MB RAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2048 MB SWAP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;100 GB HDD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1000 GB Bandwith&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 IP Adress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;



**Terms and Conditions**

    You must not use your VPS for any illegal purposes.
    We are using fraud records to review our order.
    If you have any bad reputations at fraud records, we can not offer you a VPS.

 
 
**Registration**
&lt;p&gt;Registrations is not opened yet, but you can already secure your beta account today: (https://board.serverlux.de/topic/19-registration-for-the-beta-test/)&lt;/p&gt;
